headline: Rollins (NYSE:ROL) Posts Q1 Sales In Line With Estimates
summary: Pest control company Rollins (NYSE:ROL) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2025, with sales up 9.9% year on year to $822.5 million. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.22 per share was in line with analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Rollins: Q1 Earnings Snapshot
summary: ATLANTA (AP) — Rollins Inc. ROL) on Wednesday reported first-quarter earnings of $105.2 million. The Atlanta-based company said it had profit of 22 cents per share.
